 paymentprocessing platform can complete the transaction within seconds enterprise level account management customers can add and customize permissions for their employees manage payments and revenues and withdraw funds to their linked bank accounts with ease powered by cloud using openstack cloudcomputing architecture as a foundation we developed our own cloudbased platform to power cerapay’s robust and scalable processing services safe and secure with bankgrade security all customer information is encrypted with bit encryption and stored on our secured servers   fincera inc filing and notices  fincera home who we are board of directors senior management team employee perspectives what we do overview nationwide network cerapay ceravest truship autochekk investor relations news and updates presentations and financial statements notices faqs blog contact english english  notices news and updates presentations and financial statements notices faqs  fincera  annual report  annual meeting of shareholders proxy card    notice of annual meeting of shareholders    corporate charters  audit governance and compensation committees   fincera inc home  fincera fkaautochina international  home who we are board of directors senior management team employee perspectives what we do overview nationwide network cerapay ceravest truship autochekk investor relations news and updates presentations and financial statements notices faqs blog contact english english  fincera ® fkaautochina international is a leading provider of innovative webbased financing and ecommerce services for small and mediumsized businesses and individuals in china see details fincera ® currently operates online financing and ecommerce platforms cerapay ®ceravest ®truship tm and autochekk tm see details  staff members and a network of branch offices in  provinces municipalities and autonomous regions form one of the countrys largest support networks see details news releasesmore fincera fka autochina international 