 small businesses in china essentially providing virtual business credit cards that can both send and receive payments ceravest ® is an online peertopeer lending platform that provides shortterm loans for small businesses operating in china truship tm is an ecommerce and shipping marketplace platform for the trucking industry that helps businesses connect and trade efficiently autochekk tm is an ecommerce platform focused on passenger cars and designed to streamline the consumer’s purchase and maintenance experience   fincera inc board of directors  fincera home who we are board of directors senior management team employee perspectives what we do overview nationwide network cerapay ceravest truship autochekk investor relations news and updates presentations and financial statements notices faqs blog contact english english  board of directors board of directors senior management team employee perspectives yong hui li ceo and chairman james sha director diana liu director leon chen director spencer li director yong hui li chairman and chief executive officer yong hui li has served as fincera’s chairman and chief executive officer and as a member of fincera’s board of directors since april  mr li is the founder chairman and chief executive officer of fincera inc and hebei kaiyuan real estate development co ltd “hebei kaiyuan” which he founded in july  and november  respectively from  to  mr li oversaw hebei kaiyuan’s development of the largest steelframed construction project in hebei province consisting of residential complexes office towers and an upscale shopping mall totaling over one million square feet subsequently heibei kaiyuan completed the development of the kaiyuan finance center in  a multiuse building with office spaces and a fivestar hotel managed by hilton in  mr li pioneered the commercial vehicle leasing business in china when he founded shijiazhuang hitech zone kaiyuan auto trade co a precursor to fincera’s legacy leasing business mr li graduated fro